													{
														m_id = 1736259620
													}
													m_sNote = ""
													m_commentText = "But if we haven\'t been using a non-idle animation for some time (let\'s say... 500ms...) then we don\'t need to do any of that weightlist switching business, so let\'s bypass it entirely.\n\n\"Attacking\" is not considered to break idle. Landing, moving, etc. do, because those are the animations we want to show through the non-active arm in attack anims."
